{"tid":521512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[朋友妻] 美重磅新書再爆料 TRUMP曾偷吃朋友妻子","createTime":"2018-01-06T15:31:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T03:49:02.000Z","uid":24140,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"18d78ec3ec5c74ef35a320bcf28c4b738d748c1f","tid":521512,"uid":24140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:31:57.000Z","msg":"據英國每日郵報（Daily Mail）報導，一本由前記者沃爾夫（Michael Wolff）執筆、經專訪百餘名重量級人士集結而成，並即將於9號在美出版的新書《烈燄與怒火：川普白宮揭密》（Fire and Fury: Inside the Trump White House），近日掀起網路與媒體火爆話題。繼先前多筆爆料後，如今更爆出川普（Donald Trump）在迎娶梅蘭妮亞（Melania Trump）後，曾出軌「睡了」朋友的妻子。曾為了誘惑朋友的妻子，而他利用忌妒心理陷害友人，讓對方妻子和他發生性關係。<br />\n<br />\n沃爾夫在新書中，將川普誘惑人妻的過程鉅細靡遺地呈現，「先由秘書邀請友人來公司，並事先開啟會議室內電話的免池聽筒，並在友人抵達後，不斷地詢問其性生活，更露骨地表示，他待會有幾名從洛杉磯來的女孩，你們可以上去房間內好好玩一玩。」而友人並不知道，這所有的對話內容，都讓已被川普洗腦的妻子聽到，因此認定丈夫裡外不一。書中更寫道，川普曾公開表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">「睡友人的妻子，是人生中最值得的事情之一。」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-01-06/656/20180106001832.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-01-06%2F656%2F20180106001832.jpg&h=e904dc37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n面臨爆料內容如雨後春筍般浮現，美國總統川普又一次面臨公關與信任危機。（圖/路透社）<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.chinatimes.com/newsphoto/2018-01-06/656/20180106001834.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.chinatimes.com%2Fnewsphoto%2F2018-01-06%2F656%2F20180106001834.jpg&h=2f6bd5b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n以爆料川普與其白宮秘辛而爆紅、新書《烈燄與怒火》作者沃爾夫上新聞接受專訪。（圖/路透社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180106001817-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20180106001817-260408&d=dn0RRCmRY%2FO3t512OqD4d%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=8b6b2009\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20180106001817-260408</a>"},{"pid":"6fb7e8ba3acb41c35e3ea21d03d26de431f6ac77","tid":521512,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"朋友妻"},{"pid":"ac5c750fab9a5976c0f10bc2629de8442e0362f7","tid":521512,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6fb7e8ba3acb41c35e3ea21d03d26de431f6ac77","tid":521512,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:33:35.000Z","msg":"朋友妻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:38:01.000Z","msg":"咪走雞"},{"pid":"6f3b0d1193cb7da0695afa5cb53357eefca8d666","tid":521512,"uid":44073,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:39:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b4677ec408a35480ab66db77ee2ed2fc5e279089","tid":521512,"uid":121131,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:41:09.000Z","msg":"唔個點解<br />\n硬係覺得佢會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420fb8cb513ae86ec7de7a9d0b26771429c6e7e2","tid":521512,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T15:44:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea2a9cd406906a84c3efeeae4683d5e2e6ff3b6f","tid":521512,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"話希拉里同奧巴馬做過愛都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c23fde1f87bd7092761b38ad9d4e9dd6f3bdfae","tid":521512,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:34:40.000Z","msg":"好賤"},{"pid":"be375a9a0c936034467452f558a976b828e089bf","tid":521512,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ea2a9cd406906a84c3efeeae4683d5e2e6ff3b6f","tid":521512,"uid":60545,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:27:05.000Z","msg":"話希拉里同奧巴馬做過愛都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:44:23.000Z","msg":"諗起之前林太同梁先生個痴線故 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a238bac32e0b29